  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 はっぴーばーすでーだにゃ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――七月七日　朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――七月七日　朝",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふ～ん。今日は～芽衣の～お誕生日～\nお誕生日は～ウキウキ～ラッキ～早起きハッピ～ピ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふんふんふ～ん。今日は～芽衣の～お誕生日～\nお誕生日は～ウキウキ～ラッキ～早起きハッピ～ピ～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0000000437,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8866.666623,
          "startTime": 20.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……おはよう、芽衣。今日は朝からテンションが\n高いわね。あなたも今からランニング？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふわぁ……おはよう、芽衣。今日は朝からテンションが\n高いわね。あなたも今からランニング？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2666667104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、芽衣はね、宅配便を待ってるの！\n家族が誕生日プレゼントを送ってくれたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ううん、芽衣はね、宅配便を待ってるの！\n家族が誕生日プレゼントを送ってくれたんだ～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2666667104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　そういえば今日は芽衣の誕生日だったわね\nお誕生日おめでとう、芽衣",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はっ！　そういえば今日は芽衣の誕生日だったわね\nお誕生日おめでとう、芽衣",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6999997895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、瑠依ちゃん\nお誕生日の朝はワクワクして早起きしちゃうんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ありがとう、瑠依ちゃん\nお誕生日の朝はワクワクして早起きしちゃうんだよね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8666664561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ手に持っているその箱って……\nもしかして、芽衣へのお誕生日プレゼント！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ねぇねぇ手に持っているその箱って……\nもしかして、芽衣へのお誕生日プレゼント！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1666664561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、ごめんなさい。これは父の日のプレゼントなの\n忙しくて、だいぶ遅くなっちゃったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふっ、ごめんなさい。これは父の日のプレゼントなの\n忙しくて、だいぶ遅くなっちゃったけど……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5333331228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣へのプレゼントは優とすみれと一緒に\n用意したから、後で三人で部屋に持って行くわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "芽衣へのプレゼントは優とすみれと一緒に\n用意したから、後で三人で部屋に持って行くわね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4999997895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ私はランニングのついでに\nこの荷物を郵便局に届けて来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それじゃあ私はランニングのついでに\nこの荷物を郵便局に届けて来るわ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1999997895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "待って！　芽衣も行く！　プレゼントが届くのを\n待ちきれないから郵便局まで取りに行こうかな～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "待って！　芽衣も行く！　プレゼントが届くのを\n待ちきれないから郵便局まで取りに行こうかな～って",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5666664561,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8433.3332896,
          "startTime": 91.9999997457
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　手続きもなしに郵便局まで行ったところで\n荷物は受け取れない気が……ちょっと、聞いてる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "え？　手続きもなしに郵便局まで行ったところで\n荷物は受け取れない気が……ちょっと、聞いてる！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7666664561,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6133.333289600003,
          "startTime": 97.8999997457
        }
      ]
    },
