    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ～、朝から運動すると気持ちがいいな。瑠依ちゃん\nのプレゼントも無事、宅配に出せて良かったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふぅ～、朝から運動すると気持ちがいいな。瑠依ちゃん\nのプレゼントも無事、宅配に出せて良かったね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1666761201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3000094534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の荷物はまだ郵便局に届いていなかったみたいで\n残念だったわね。午後の配達になるのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "芽衣の荷物はまだ郵便局に届いていなかったみたいで\n残念だったわね。午後の配達になるのかしら？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2333427867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.3000094534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "荷物が届くまでのワクワクする時間が伸びたって\n思えば、なんだかオトクな気がするでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "荷物が届くまでのワクワクする時間が伸びたって\n思えば、なんだかオトクな気がするでしょ？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3666761201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.0000094534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "今日は一日中ワクワクでドキドキで\nハッピーな気持ちで過ごせそうだよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今日は一日中ワクワクでドキドキで\nハッピーな気持ちで過ごせそうだよ～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0000094534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.6333427867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そういう前向きなところが芽衣の長所よね\n私達からのプレゼントもお楽しみに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふっ、そういう前向きなところが芽衣の長所よね\n私達からのプレゼントもお楽しみに",
        "id": ""
      },
